spearmanr_004 = spearmanr(pd.to_numeric(exRNAQC004['Femto_conc'], errors = "coerce"), pd.to_numeric(exRNAQC004['EndovsERCC'], errors = "coerce"), axis = 0)[0]
pearsonr_004 = pearsonr(pd.to_numeric(exRNAQC004['Femto_conc'], errors = "coerce"), pd.to_numeric(exRNAQC004['EndovsERCC'], errors = "coerce"))[0]

     #size=6, color='black')

sns_plot_004.set(xscale="log", yscale="log")

sns_plot_004.axes.set_title("exRNAQC004 (kits - DNase treated) \n Spearman = %.2f" % (spearmanr_004), fontsize=16)
fig_004 = sns_plot_004.get_figure()
